After a VERY long search, we are finally homeowners! 😭 

We cannot wait to fill this place with all the love, music, and memories for years to come…OH and my incredible parents! We are beyond excited to have them make the move from TX to be under one roof with us and watch Piper grow up 🥹 It’s been my dream to be close to my parents and raise my children near them and I feel like all my dreams are coming true before my eyes. I am so blessed. We’re so happy to be bringing you all along on this next chapter with us 🙏🏻🤍 

P.S- stay tuned to see how we renovate and make this beautiful space our own! 😍

Back when I was pregnant with Piper 🥹 Feeling so nostalgic about my whole journey as “The Stairwell Siren” and how I won’t be haunting this particular stairwell much longer. This place got me through so much; a pandemic, a pregnancy, a sleepless and very hard postpartum, and more. The highest of highs and the lowest of lows. And through it all, singing in here was my release. Forever grateful to this dirty garage stairwell for making me who I am today 🤍
S/O to my mama for raising me around the best music that would influence my own taste and sound for the rest of my life 🫶🏻 @thecranberries
